pageTitle: Classical Piano Midi Page - MP3 Files
textBeforeTable: Most of my Midi Files are available in MP3. The Midi sequences are played on a digital piano (Roland HP 330e) and recorded via an audio interface.The recording is made with 44,1 Hz and 128 kBit/s. Some of them are played on the virtual piano Pianoteq . Use the right mouse click to save a MP3 file. Please read the copyright notice before using the MP3 files.
